snippet.title: Princess and Frog for the Atari 8-bit family
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

Princess and Frog (aka. "The Princess and the Frog") is a Frogger clone.

You play as a cursed who can temporarily become a prince again by getting kissed by the princess on the other side of the shore. 

You have to avoid cavaliers, jump on snakes and on crocodiles. Be aware though, sometimes the crocodiles submerge.

There are also blue frogs you hop on for bonus points.


What I think:

Really fun game, but it is tough as nails. 
Also sometimes it takes way too long till those friggin' lips appear!
